To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private AugenPriceSpike _aps;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_aps = APS(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_aps.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "augenpricespike", _aps.Current.Value);
}
